                <img src="images/about-tablet.jpg" alt="Profile Image">
            </picture>
            <div class="about-text">
              <h1 class="hello1"> OH, HELLO THERE!</h1>
              <p>
                
                My name is <span class="vira">Vira</span> <span class="romanko">Romanko</span> and I am a junior front-end developer with design passion. I believe that great design is practical and oriented on the end user. 
                Aside from designing and coding, I love music, photography and wake boarding!
                My main goal in the work process is to break down big tasks into small ones and ensure that customers are satisfied with the end deliverables.  
          
          
                <span class="vision"> Share my vision?  Take a look at my works</span>
              </p>
            </div>

      </div>
     
     
    

    </section>

